# Clean Markdown Format

## Structure

- MD025/single-title
- MD001/heading-increment
- MD022/blanks-around-headings → 1 blank line before/after
- MD024/no-duplicate-heading
- MD031/blanks-around-fences → 1 blank line before/after
- MD012/no-multiple-blanks

## Formatting

- MD004/ul-style
- MD030/list-marker-space
- MD032/blanks-around-lists → 1 blank line before/after if surrounded by text or blocks
- MD040/fenced-code-language → always specify language, use `text` as default
- MD034/no-bare-urls
- MD009/no-trailing-spaces
- MD013/line-length (max 120)
- MD047/single-trailing-newline

## Lists

- Simple lists: no extra blank lines between items
- Lists with blocks: 1 blank line before the block
- Numbered lists: consistent format (1. 2. 3.)

## Tables

- Columns visually aligned with spaces
- Alignment: `:---` (left), `:---:` (center), `---:` (right)
